{
  "stem": "19795.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once, I washed, you know, with a little bit of water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I got, you know, like the ice parts from my hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't at the time, because I cut my hair with a-- a knife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was, I think, in the-- in the basement when I was by the-- by the man with the, with the Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So with a knife, I cut, you know, just a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I had long hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But just the same, you can't keep-- [? but ?] tangled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] How can I look after so many time, and, and all this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I look not bad now at this age after 50 years, so--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had my hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My natural color, sure-- at this time to color?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not very thin-- normal, normal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after so many-- so long, not, you know, not proper eat, not proper getting not proper sleep and not to get washed and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But right away, I got on the chubby side, start to eat bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't finish a bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I finished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I still want some more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were happy and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I start to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't cry all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I start to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I going to do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where I going to go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to who I going to go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what is going to be with me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In there, the family wanted I should go with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't want, because I had them enough in the attic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me, I want to get [LAUGHS] finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
